entries.journal_entry_description: You're on Hunnos Jarkey's trail. Follow the trail until you find the escaped murderer himself.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Find out what the Muskeg's want from Hunnos Jarkey. What is their connection to the escaped murderer?
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Muskeg Gungans are proving to be tough to crack, but keep it and find out what they know about Hunnos Jarkey.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The Muskeg say nothing to you. They fight and die without revealing anything, but they can't keep it up. Continue your assault on them.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Dubbin Sharr is the local Zealot Chief of the Muskeg in the Theed area. He is your last chance to find out what the Muskeg want with Hunnos Jarkey.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Defeat Dubbin Sharr, a Zealot Chief of the Muskeg
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You find a note on Chief Dubbin. From it you learn that the Muskeg wanted Hunnos Jarkey to assassinate members of the Naboo human government. Hunnos refused and went to hideout with the Skaak Tippers.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Note on Muskeg Zealot Chief Dubbin Sharr
entries.task04_message_box_text: You find a note on Chief Dubbin. From it you learn that the Muskeg wanted Hunnos Jarkey to assassinate members of the Naboo human government. Hunnos refused and went to hideout with the Skaak Tippers.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Go to the Skaak Tipper compound and convince them to reveal what they know about where Hunnos is hiding.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Hunnos was with the Skaak Tippers for a very short time,  and then moved on to the Mummers.
entries.task06_message_box_text: Hunnos was only with the Skaak Tippers for a very short time. They think he went to the Mummers.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Go to the Mummer bunker and find out what they know about Hunnos.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: The Mummers revealed that Hunnos went to hide out on a ranch not far from Theed. He is still there. Report this back to Lieutenant Khartoor.
entries.task08_message_box_text: The Mummers revealed that Hunnos went to hide out on a ranch not far from Theed. He is still there. Report this back to Lieutenant Khartoor.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Report back to Lt. Khartoor with what you've learned.
